{
  "text": "Using both the classic lead acetate reactivity test for H 2 S detection and a fluorescentbased probe, WSP5 [CITATION_1] , we confirmed that this phenotypic reversion was concurrent with increased H 2 S production, comparable to wild type (Fig. 1c) . In contrast, significant levels of H 2 S remained undetectable in \u0394mstA till OD 600 1.5.",
